Interface EventServiceBindingDescriptor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BindingDescriptor

    public interface EventServiceBindingDescriptor
extends BindingDescriptor
    This interface contains a set of Event bindings that make up the set of events exposed on a particular event transport.
